# Minecraft Version(s): 26.1.x
## Changes:
- Lang Files are now getting automatically synced with crowdin with new releases
- Creeper Cat variant now drops Gun Powder instead of String
- Embroidery Cat variant now drops random Dyes instead of String
- Soul Cat variant now drops Soul Sand instead of String
- Added Red, Spotted Red & Muddy Red Pig variants (Spawn in the same biomes as vanilla warm variant)

